Escape from here.

32
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:46,319
No.

33
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:47,719
Nan Xing, it's too dangerous.

34
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:49,319
They're no mere bandits.

35
00:01:49,439 --> 00:01:51,120
