36
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:55,159
I will definitely come back for you.

37
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,719
Trust me.

38
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,480
Nan Xing.

39
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:13,919
Over there, chase.

40
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:21,120
Princess.

41
