Come in.

59
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,839
Your Highness.

60
00:04:52,399 --> 00:04:54,439
There are some clues to
officials' private trade

61
00:04:54,439 --> 00:04:55,319
with foreign tribes.

62
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,600
Got it.

63
00:04:58,079 --> 00:05:01,160
Prepare some new clothes
for the Princess of Sheng State.

64
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,680
Princess of Sheng State?

65
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:09,199
Sure, I'll prepare it now.

66
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:14,519
(Your Highness?)

67
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:16,959
(He is a prince of Yu State.)

68
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:20,399
