106
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:55,759
Any evidence?

107
00:06:56,519 --> 00:06:57,439
Of course.

108
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:58,680
The diplomatic marriage pact.

109
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,279
(Oops.)

110
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,800
